{
  "text": "The value of \u039b 2n is derived from the above I 2n via (5.13). It has previously been shown by [CITATION_1] that so long as z h max a logarithmic dependence upon z will be exhibited. In fact, this can be re-expressed in terms of the function \u03bb k , which is defined in equation (19) of that article. It is given by",
